@host = http://localhost:3000
@baseUrl = {{host}}/api/v1
@token = Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### ============================================
### KNOWLEDGE MODULE - Knowledge Management (Zettels)
### ============================================

### ZETTELS - List Zettels
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/zettels?page=1&limit=20&search=typescript
Authorization: {{token}}

### ZETTELS - Get Zettel
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/zettels/:zettelId
Authorization: {{token}}

### ZETTELS - Create Zettel
POST {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/zettels
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "TypeScript Advanced Patterns",
  "content": "Understanding advanced patterns in TypeScript including generics...",
  "tags": ["typescript", "patterns", "programming"],
  "relatedZettels": ["zettel-uuid-1"]
}

### ZETTELS - Update Zettel
PUT {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/zettels/:zettelId
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "TypeScript Advanced Patterns - Updated",
  "content": "Enhanced content with more examples..."
}

### ZETTELS - Delete Zettel
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/zettels/:zettelId
Authorization: {{token}}

### TAGS - List Tags
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/tags
Authorization: {{token}}

### SEARCH - Search Knowledge
GET {{baseUrl}}/knowledge/search?q=typescript&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: {{token}}

### Notes:
### - All endpoints require authentication
### - Zettels are interconnected knowledge nodes
### - Replace UUIDs with actual IDs from your database
